snippet.textDisplay:
Please stop pretending that Star Citizen ISN'T out. The Single Player game Squadron 42 isn't. BUT the Star Citizen MMO IS out and playable. Lots of people are playing it and enjoying it and have been for a few years now even though it's still very much beta. Stop conflating the two and acting like it isn't out in any form.

I say this as someone who Kickstarted the game a while ago and doesn't play it because I kickstarted for the single player game. ...and YES I am getting sick of Squadron 42 being pushed back again and again but please direct the anger/mocking/etc to where it belongs.
